Data Structures¶

This page details the data structures used for the translation of Makka Pakka to assembly. Structures are split into their phase of compilation. More information about the phases of compilation can be found in the Compilation Process page.

See also

  • Public API

Parsing Structures¶

class makka_pakka.parsing.parsing_structures.MKPKFunction(name: str, arguments: List[str], content: List[str])¶

A data strcture to encapsulate code functions used in makka pakka.

class makka_pakka.parsing.parsing_structures.MKPKData(name: str, value: int | str, type: MKPKDataType)¶

A data structure to encapsulate constant data used in makka pakka

class makka_pakka.parsing.parsing_structures.MKPKDataType¶

Identifies the data type of a MKPKData object.

class makka_pakka.parsing.parsing_structures.MKPKGadget(memory_location: str, content: List[str])¶

A data structure to encapsulate ROP gadgets used in makka pakka.

class makka_pakka.parsing.parsing_structures.MKPKMetaData(label: str, value: str)¶

A data structure to encapsulate metadata used in makka pakka

class makka_pakka.parsing.parsing_structures.MKPKIR¶

An intermediate representation of the makka pakka programming language to be populated during the parsing phase.

class makka_pakka.parsing.parsing_structures.MKPKLines(data: List[str] = [], code: List[str] = [], gadgets: List[str] = [], metadata: List[str] = [])¶

A data structure to hold the raw text lines from a .mkpk in their respective heading sections.

Processing Structures¶

class makka_pakka.processing.processing_structures.MKPKCode(data: List[MKPKData], code: List[str], gadgets: MKPKGadget)¶

Encapsulates the result of the processing phase.

Exceptions¶

exception makka_pakka.exceptions.exceptions.MKPKCyclicDependency(headline: str, description: str, type: int)¶

Alerts the caller when a cyclic dependency is detected in a DirectedGraph.

exception makka_pakka.exceptions.exceptions.MKPKError(headline: str, description: str, type: int)¶

An exception class which standardised the format of MakkaPakka error messgaes.

exception makka_pakka.exceptions.exceptions.MKPKIntegratingError(headline: str, description: str, type: int)¶

Alerts the caller of an error while integrating makka pakka code.

exception makka_pakka.exceptions.exceptions.MKPKInvalidParameter(name: str, func: str, value: Any)¶

Alerts the callers when a parameter passed to MakkaPakka function is invalid, likely because it is of the incorrect type.

exception makka_pakka.exceptions.exceptions.MKPKLinkingError(headline: str, description: str, type: int)¶

Alerts the caller of an error while linking makka pakka code.

exception makka_pakka.exceptions.exceptions.MKPKNameError(headline: str, description: str, type: int)¶

Alerts the caller of an error in a name used in makka pakka code.

exception makka_pakka.exceptions.exceptions.MKPKParsingError(headline: str, description: str, type: int)¶

Alerts the caller of an error while parsing makka pakka code.

exception makka_pakka.exceptions.exceptions.MKPKProcessingError(headline: str, description: str, type: int)¶

Alerts the caller of an error while processing makka pakka code.
